I had planned to leave this ridiculous site.. because of several uncouth individuals who think the Comanche and Lakota Raids were unjust... Well, it hurts to be called a War Eagle... and a Trapper Scalper!  I told everyone to hang around the Fort... but no-o-ooo!  The Chief wanted more ponies... so I went.  I could have stayed in the village and swept dog droppings... chewed Peyote.. better yet I could have run to the Indian Territory!<br>
A lot of guys got Eagle Feathers for their deeds... What did I get...PTSD (Pony Turd Scoop Detail)?<br>
Like my grandfather used to say, &quot;It is a good day to cry!&quot;<br><br>
Flaming Arrow
